  <brief_title>Systemic Inflammation Versus Acute Pain in Total Knee Arthroplasty (TKA)</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Relation Between Systemic Inflammatory Markers and Acute Pain in TKA</official_title>
  <sponsors>
